ISLAMABAD, Sep 13 (APP): The employees and staff of the Ministry of Maritime Affairs has donated Rs 10 million to the Prime Minister’s Flood Relief Fund, the PM Office said Tuesday.
Maritime Affairs Minister Syed Faisal Sabzwari presented the cheque worth Rs 10 million to Prime Minister Shehbaz Sharif to supplement the government’s relief and rehabilitation activities in the flood-hit areas.
